    <input type="radio" name="rather" value="C"> Art Museum<br>
    <input type="radio" name="rather" value="D"> Shop<br>
  </p>
  <br>
  
  <h3 class = "questions">How would you describe your fashion sense?</h3>
  <p class = "options">
    <input type="radio" name="fashion" value="A"> Casual and functional<br>
    <input type="radio" name="fashion" value="B"> Relaxed and comfortable<br>
    <input type="radio" name="fashion" value="C"> Classic and Chic<br>
    <input type="radio" name="fashion" value="D"> Trendy and expressive<br>
  </p>
    <br>
    
  <h3 class = "questions">What type of weather do you most enjoy?</h3>
