    <input type="radio" name="stay" value="C"> Quaint Apartment with a balcony<br>
    <input type="radio" name="stay" value="D"> Highrise with a cityscape view<br>
  </p>
    <br>
    
  <h3 class = questions>What word best describes you</h3>
